{"Id":480,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":48,"Text":"说情者的说情，将无益於他们。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":49,"Text":"他们怎么退避这教训呢？"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":50,"Text":"他们好像一群惊慌的驴子，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":51,"Text":"刚逃避了一只狮子一样。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":52,"Text":"不然，他们中的每个人都希望获得一些展开的天经。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":53,"Text":"绝不然，他们不畏惧后世！"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":54,"Text":"真的，这《古兰经》确是一个教诲！"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":55,"Text":"谁愿意，谁记忆它，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":56,"Text":"他们只因真主的意欲而记忆它。他是应受敬畏的，他是宜於赦宥的。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"我以复活日盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"我以自责的灵魂盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"难道人猜想我绝不能集合他的骸骨吗？"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"不然，（我将集合他的骸骨），而且能使他的每个手指复原。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"不然，人欲长此放荡下去。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"他问复活日在甚么时候。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"当眼目昏花，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"月亮昏暗，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"日月相合的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"在那日，人将说：逃到哪里去呢？"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"绝不然，绝无任何避难所。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"在那日，唯你的主那里，有安定之所。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"在那日，各人将被告知自己前前后后做过的事情。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"不然，各人对自己就是明证，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"即使他多方托辞。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"你不要摇动你的舌头，以便你仓卒地诵读它。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"集合它和诵读它，确是我的责任。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"当我诵读它的时候，你当静听我的诵读。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"然后解释它，也是我的责任。"}]}